WEBVTT

00:01.035 --> 00:04.672
Daniel: ONE DAY OF THE WEEK
I HAVE NO LECTURES,

00:04.705 --> 00:06.674
NO OFFICE HOURS,
NO OBLIGATIONS OF ANY KIND...

00:06.707 --> 00:09.343
...THE ONE DAY THAT I-I GET
A LITTLE SOLITUDE, YOU KNOW,

00:09.377 --> 00:11.179
A LITTLE "ME" TIME, A CHANCE
TO DO SOME ACTUAL WRITING.

00:11.212 --> 00:12.413
HALEY TWISTED MY ARM.

00:12.446 --> 00:14.282
YOUR ARM IS MINE TO TWIST,
NOT HALEY'S.

00:14.315 --> 00:16.016
DID HE EVEN SAY
WHAT THIS WAS ABOUT?

00:16.050 --> 00:17.351
[ APPLAUSE ]

00:17.385 --> 00:18.686
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]

00:18.719 --> 00:21.122
DANIEL, IT IS MY HONOR
TO INFORM YOU

00:21.155 --> 00:23.791
THAT YOU HAVE BEEN AWARDED
THIS YEAR'S DAVENPORT PRIZE

00:23.824 --> 00:26.294
FOR EXPLORATION IN SCIENCE.

00:26.327 --> 00:28.796
I-I SWEAR,
I KNEW NOTHING ABOUT THIS.

00:28.829 --> 00:30.931
AND, AS I'M SURE
YOU ARE AWARE,

00:30.964 --> 00:33.267
THIS AWARD IS NOT JUST
ABOUT THE LAURELS

00:33.301 --> 00:35.436
YOU BRING TO YOURSELF
AND THE UNIVERSITY.

00:35.469 --> 00:40.474
IT'S ALSO ABOUT THE $50,000
CHECK THAT GOES ALONG WITH IT.

00:40.508 --> 00:43.444
TO DANIEL PIERCE.

00:43.477 --> 00:44.745
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

00:46.347 --> 00:47.481
[ CORK POPS ]

00:47.515 --> 00:49.483
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

00:49.517 --> 00:52.253
[ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

00:58.826 --> 01:00.461
DANIEL.

01:00.494 --> 01:02.496
HOW COULD YOU
BLINDSIDE ME LIKE THAT?

01:02.530 --> 01:05.233
YOU ARE MAKING ME LOOK BAD
IN FRONT OF THE CHANCELLOR.

01:05.266 --> 01:09.570
THE MAN PUT YOU UP FOR THIS
PRIZE, FOR GOODNESS SAKES.

01:09.603 --> 01:11.905
JUST ONE HANDSHAKE.
THAT'S ALL I'M ASKING.

01:11.939 --> 01:13.241
KATE.

01:13.274 --> 01:16.110
PLEASE TELL ME
YOU'RE HERE ABOUT A CASE.

01:16.144 --> 01:18.846
YEPaul: MS. MORETTI,--

01:18.879 --> 01:20.614
I AGREED TO ALLOW DANIEL
TO CONSULT WITH THE FBI

01:20.648 --> 01:22.616
SO LONG AS IT DIDN'T INTERFERE
WITH HIS ACADEMIC DUTIES.

01:22.650 --> 01:24.318
AND RIGHT NOW YOU ARE
INTERFERING WITH --

01:24.352 --> 01:26.154
ACTUALLY, I'M HERE
TO TALK TO YOU.

01:27.288 --> 01:28.689
TO ME?

01:28.722 --> 01:31.492
YEAH, LISTEN, A JOGGER
WAS FOUND SHOT IN THE BACK

01:31.525 --> 01:33.127
IN THE NATIONAL FOREST
PRESERVE.

01:33.161 --> 01:34.728
WE'RE HAVING TROUBLE
MAKING AN I.D.

01:34.762 --> 01:36.697
THERE'S NO WALLET ON HIM,
NO MATCH ON THE FINGERPRINTS.

01:36.730 --> 01:37.831
WHAT HAS THIS GOT TO DO
WITH HIM?

01:37.865 --> 01:39.333
ALL WE'VE GOT TO GO ON

01:39.367 --> 01:40.701
ARE SOME TATTOOS
ON THE BODY

01:40.734 --> 01:42.370
WHICH APPEAR TO BE
RELIGIOUS IN NATURE,

01:42.403 --> 01:45.206
AND DEAN HALEY'S COURSE
ON SPIRITUAL ICONOGRAPHY

01:45.239 --> 01:47.875
WAS ONE OF THE BEST CLASSES
I EVER TOOK.

01:47.908 --> 01:49.610
I'M FLATTERED
YOU REMEMBER.

01:49.643 --> 01:51.145
ANYHOW, I'M HOPING YOU COULD
TAKE A LOOK AT THE TATTOOS,

01:51.179 --> 01:53.514
LET ME KNOW IF THERE'S
ANYTHING ABOUT THEM

01:53.547 --> 01:55.115
THAT COULD HELP ME
I.D. THE VICTIM.

01:55.149 --> 01:56.550
I CONFESS I'VE ALWAYS BEEN

01:56.584 --> 01:58.619
SOMETHING
OF AN ARMCHAIR DETECTIVE.

01:58.652 --> 02:00.621
PAUL, YOU COULDN'T POSSIBLY.
THE CHANCELLOR.

02:00.654 --> 02:02.456
I JUST TELL HIM THAT

02:02.490 --> 02:04.057
IT'S A MURDER
INVESTIGATION, RIGHT?

02:04.091 --> 02:05.626
COME ON, DANIEL.

02:05.659 --> 02:07.060
YOU'LL NEED TO KEEP HIM
ENTERTAINED WHILE I'M GONE.

02:07.094 --> 02:08.262
Help me.

02:08.296 --> 02:11.399
WH-- UH, DEAN HALEY, UH,
ACTUALLY,

02:11.432 --> 02:14.034
OUR VICTIM MAY HAVE SUFFERED
SOME HEAD INJURIES,

02:14.067 --> 02:16.804
SO I DO NEED A BRAIN SPECIALIST
TO REVIEW THE X-RAYS.

02:16.837 --> 02:19.740
YOU COULDN'T POSSIBLY SPARE
DANIEL, UH, JUST FOR AN HOUR?

02:19.773 --> 02:23.411
I'M SURE THE CHANCELLOR
WILL UNDERSTAND.

02:23.444 --> 02:26.580
THIS IS VERY EXCITING.

02:26.614 --> 02:28.081
[ RETCHING ]

02:28.115 --> 02:30.083
[ SPITTING ]

02:30.117 --> 02:33.254
OH.
[ SNIFFS ]

02:33.287 --> 02:35.256
PROBABLY A LITTLE
TOO MUCH BUBBLY

02:35.289 --> 02:37.090
AT THE RECEPTION,
I THINK.

02:37.124 --> 02:40.561
OKAY. UM, LET'S SEE
WHAT WE'VE GOT HERE.

02:40.594 --> 02:44.932
WELL, THE ANGEL APPEARS TO DRAW
FROM CHRISTIAN INFLUENCES,

02:44.965 --> 02:48.402
BUT THESE EIGHT WINGS

02:48.436 --> 02:51.405
PROBABLY REPRESENT
THE EIGHT ARMS OF SHIVA,

02:51.439 --> 02:53.106
THE HINDU GOD
OF DESTRUCTION.

02:53.140 --> 02:54.775
AH. UH-HUH.

02:54.808 --> 02:57.110
WHICH WOULD MAKE
THIS SIMIAN FIGURE

02:57.144 --> 02:59.413
REPRESENTATIVE OF HANUMAN,
THE HINDU MONKEY GOD.

02:59.447 --> 03:02.583
AND I'D SAY THESE NUMBERS
REPRESENT

03:02.616 --> 03:05.786
THE BOOK OF RUTH,
CHAPTER 1, VERSE 16.

03:05.819 --> 03:08.121
"THY PEOPLE
SHALL BE MY PEOPLE."

03:08.155 --> 03:09.657
THE WORDS NAOMI SPOKE

03:09.690 --> 03:11.024
WHEN CONVERTING TO THE FAITH
OF HER MOTHER-IN-LAW.

03:11.058 --> 03:13.594
SO, YOU PROBABLY
WANT TO MAKE INQUIRIES

03:13.627 --> 03:15.296
AT A LOCAL HINDU TEMPLE

03:15.329 --> 03:17.965
FREQUENTED BY CONVERTS FROM
THE JUDEO-CHRISTIAN TRADITION.

03:17.998 --> 03:20.634
YOU MIGHT WANT TO INQUIRE
AT A LOCAL METHADONE CLINIC.

03:20.668 --> 03:22.303
WHY DO YOU SAY THAT?

03:22.336 --> 03:24.638
I THINK IT'S A PRETTY SAFE BET
YOUR VICTIM HERE WAS A JUNKIE.

03:24.672 --> 03:27.308
"MONKEY ON MY BACK," IS A COMMON
TERM FOR HEROIN ADDICTION.

03:27.341 --> 03:30.811
1:16 IS PROBABLY
A SOBRIETY DATE,

03:30.844 --> 03:32.313
WHICH A LOT OF ADDICTS
TATTOO ON THEIR BODIES.

03:32.346 --> 03:33.814
IF HE GOT SOBER
WITH THE HELP OF METHADONE,

03:33.847 --> 03:35.816
MAYBE SOMEBODY AT A CLINIC
WOULD RECOGNIZE HIM.

03:35.849 --> 03:40.220
OF COURSE, I DON'T WANT TO...
CONTRADICT THE EXPERT.

03:40.254 --> 03:42.523
[ RETCHES ]

03:49.563 --> 03:52.333
Kate: I'M HERE ABOUT YOUR SON,
MRS. BAKER.

03:52.366 --> 03:53.767
WHAT'S JARED DONE NOW?

03:53.801 --> 03:56.337
WELL, HE'S LISTED YOU
AS HIS EMERGENCY CONTACT

03:56.370 --> 03:59.373
ON HIS INTAKE FORM AT
THE 7th STREET METHADONE CLINIC.

04:00.441 --> 04:02.510
YOUR SON'S BODY
WAS FOUND YESTERDAY

04:02.543 --> 04:04.044
IN THE FOREST PRESERVE.

04:04.077 --> 04:08.282
IT APPEARS HE WAS MURDERED.
I'M...VERY SORRY.

04:15.122 --> 04:17.891
THANK YOU FOR BRINGING ME
THE NEWS IN PERSON.

04:21.028 --> 04:24.164
I ALWAYS THOUGHT I WOULD GET A
CALL IN THE MIDDLE OF THE NIGHT.

04:24.197 --> 04:26.033
YOU WERE
EXPECTING THIS?

04:26.066 --> 04:27.701
I TRIED EVERYTHING --

04:27.735 --> 04:32.039
THERAPISTS, REHAB,
A CLINIC IN SWITZERLAND.

04:32.072 --> 04:37.878
BUT WHEN HE TURNED 21 AND CAME
INTO HIS GRANDFATHER'S TRUST,

04:37.911 --> 04:42.015
HE HAD MONEY FOR ALL THE DRUGS
HE COULD POSSIBLY DESIRE.

04:42.049 --> 04:45.319
WHEN WAS THE LAST TIME
YOU SAW HIM?

04:45.353 --> 04:48.121
FOUR MONTHS AGO,
MAYBE FIVE.

04:48.155 --> 04:49.957
OKAY.

04:49.990 --> 04:51.692
AND DO YOU KNOW
WHERE HE WAS LIVING?

04:51.725 --> 04:54.227
WITH SOME KIND
OF RELIGIOUS CULT.

04:54.261 --> 04:57.064
IT BLED HIM
OF EVERY LAST CENT HE HAD LEFT.

04:57.097 --> 05:00.067
[ Voice breaking ] HE SAID
HE FOUND THE VOICE OF GOD

05:00.100 --> 05:02.169
AND WAS FINALLY
GETTING CLEAN.

05:05.072 --> 05:08.409
SOME GOOD
THE VOICE OF GOD DID HIM.

05:08.442 --> 05:11.244
Kate:
IT'S CALLED HAVEN HOUSE.

05:11.278 --> 05:13.581
LOOKS LIKE
SOME SORT OF COMMUNE.

05:13.614 --> 05:17.485
IT'S ALL CENTERED AROUND
THIS KID -- KYLE JENSEN.

05:17.518 --> 05:19.720
16 YEARS OLD.

05:19.753 --> 05:21.422
THEY SAY HE TALKS
DIRECTLY TO GOD.

05:21.455 --> 05:24.425
AND YOUR VICTIM GAVE ALL
HIS MONEY TO THIS WACKO CULT?

05:24.458 --> 05:26.093
ALMOST $500,000.

05:26.126 --> 05:27.094
WHAT?!

05:27.127 --> 05:28.629
THAT'S THE WAY IT WORKS.

05:28.662 --> 05:30.431
EVERYONE WHO JOINS
GIVES EVERY DIME THEY HAVE.

05:30.464 --> 05:32.265
[ LAUGHS ]
IT'S A HAVEN, ALL RIGHT --

05:32.299 --> 05:34.001
FOR ANYBODY
WITH MONEY IN THE BANK

05:34.034 --> 05:35.569
AND NO BRAIN
IN THEIR SKULL.

05:35.603 --> 05:38.572
I SWEAR, IT -- IT --
IT -- IT STAGGERS ME.

05:38.606 --> 05:40.073
MILLENNIUM
AFTER MILLENNIUM,

05:40.107 --> 05:42.275
NO MATTER HOW MANY OF THESE
CHARLATANS ARE UNMASKED,

05:42.309 --> 05:44.177
PEOPLE KEEP SHOVELING GOLD
INTO THE POCKETS

05:44.211 --> 05:45.879
OF THE NEXT CROOK
WHO CLAIMS TO SPEAK

05:45.913 --> 05:48.882
IN THE NAME OF SOME NONEXISTENT
SANTA CLAUS IN THE SKY.

05:48.916 --> 05:50.017
IT'S UNBELIEVABLE.

05:50.050 --> 05:51.118
I THOUGHT
YOU'D BE INTERESTED.

05:51.151 --> 05:52.185
DO YOU WANT TO
TAG ALONG?

05:52.219 --> 05:53.987
TRY AND STOP ME.

06:06.634 --> 06:07.768
[ ALARM CHIRPS ]

06:07.801 --> 06:11.271
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

06:11.304 --> 06:14.808
HI. ARE YOU HERE
FOR KYLE?

06:14.842 --> 06:16.644
HE'LL BE TALKING TO EVERYBODY
IN JUST A COUPLE OF MINUTES.

06:16.677 --> 06:18.546
WE'RE WITH THE FBI.

06:18.579 --> 06:21.482
THE FBI?
IS THERE SOMETHING WRONG?

06:21.515 --> 06:23.316
WE'D LIKE TO TALK
TO WHOEVER'S IN CHARGE.

06:23.350 --> 06:25.819
WELL, NOBODY'S
REALLY IN CHARGE.

06:25.853 --> 06:27.287
UM, THIS IS
TOM AND SANDY'S HOUSE,

06:27.320 --> 06:28.822
BUT THEY'RE IN
WITH KYLE RIGHT NOW.

06:28.856 --> 06:31.391
COULD THIS WAIT
TILL HE'S FINISHED?

06:31.425 --> 06:33.326
H-HE REALLY LIKES TO TELL US
WHAT GOD SAID TO HIM

06:33.360 --> 06:34.828
WHILE IT'S STILL FRESH
IN HIS HEAD.

06:34.862 --> 06:36.997
ANY CHANCE
WE COULD LISTEN

06:37.030 --> 06:38.666
TO THE WORD OF GOD
WHILE WE WAIT?

06:38.699 --> 06:40.868
EVERYONE IS WELCOME.

06:42.470 --> 06:45.573
Behave yourself,
Daniel.

06:45.606 --> 06:48.408
Tom: IT'S WONDERFUL
TO SEE ALL OF YOU HERE.

06:48.442 --> 06:50.578
SO MANY NEW FACES
HERE TODAY.

06:50.611 --> 06:53.080
I'M TOM SHELBY, AND, UH,
THIS IS MY WIFE, SANDY.

06:53.113 --> 06:55.182
HI, EVERYBODY.

06:55.215 --> 06:57.250
AND, UH,
THESE ARE THE TWO BOYS

06:57.284 --> 06:59.553
I WAS LUCKY ENOUGH
TO GET IN THE PACKAGE DEAL

06:59.587 --> 07:00.688
WHEN I MARRIED HER...

07:00.721 --> 07:03.190
...GREG AND KYLE.

07:03.223 --> 07:06.026
UH, NOW, AS MUCH AS I'D LIKE
TO BELIEVE OTHERWISE,

07:06.059 --> 07:08.696
I KNOW YOU DIDN'T COME
TO HEAR ME FLAP MY JAW,

07:08.729 --> 07:11.699
SO I'M GONNA SHUT UP
AND TURN THE FLOOR OVER TO KYLE.

07:11.732 --> 07:13.934
[ APPLAUSE ]

07:16.504 --> 07:17.838
THANKS, TOM.

07:17.871 --> 07:21.475
UM...GOD PICKS
THE CRAZIEST TIMES

07:21.509 --> 07:24.044
TO TAP ME ON THE SHOULDER
AND START TALKING.

07:24.077 --> 07:25.378
TODAY, IT WAS WHILE
I WAS DOING THE DISHES,

07:25.412 --> 07:26.880
AND I WANT TO APOLOGIZE
TO MY MOM

07:26.914 --> 07:29.717
FOR THE PITCHER I DROPPED
WHEN I CHECKED OUT.

07:29.750 --> 07:31.051
[ LAUGHTER ]

07:31.084 --> 07:33.921
TODAY, GOD TALKED TO ME
ABOUT DOUBT

07:33.954 --> 07:37.090
AND HOW IMPORTANT IT IS
FOR US NOT TO BE SCARED OF IT.

07:37.124 --> 07:39.092
HE SAID HE GAVE US DOUBT
SO THAT WE'D ALWAYS

07:39.126 --> 07:41.595
BE TRYING TO FIGURE OUT
HOW THINGS REALLY WORK,

07:41.629 --> 07:43.296
YOU KNOW, AND HOW WE CAN
MAKE THEM BETTER.

07:43.330 --> 07:47.735
NOW, THERE ARE PEOPLE
IN THIS ROOM WHO HAVE NO DOUBT,

07:47.768 --> 07:50.070
AND THAT IS
A BEAUTIFUL THING.

07:50.103 --> 07:51.705
BUT GOD ALSO TALKED TO ME

07:51.739 --> 07:54.675
ABOUT HOW BEING TOO SURE
OF ANYTHING CAN BE DANGEROUS.

07:56.276 --> 08:00.413
AND THERE IS SOMEBODY HERE
WHO HAS ONLY DOUBT...

08:00.447 --> 08:03.517
WHO DOESN'T BELIEVE
AT ALL.

08:05.853 --> 08:09.489
BUT I'M REALLY GLAD
HE'S HERE.

08:22.970 --> 08:24.504
[ SANDY SIGHS ]

08:24.538 --> 08:27.841
JARED WAS SUCH
A BEAUTIFUL PERSON.

08:27.875 --> 08:29.610
WHEN WAS THE LAST TIME
YOU SAW HIM?

08:29.643 --> 08:32.613
ABOUT 6:00
JUST YESTERDAY MORNING.

08:32.646 --> 08:34.848
HE -- HE WENT OUT
ON HIS JOG.

08:34.882 --> 08:37.951
AND YOU DIDN'T WONDER WHY HE
DIDN'T COME HOME LAST NIGHT?

08:37.985 --> 08:39.853
NO. EVERYBODY HERE
IS FREE TO COME AND GO.

08:39.887 --> 08:42.956
Nikki:
I WAS WORRIED, ACTUALLY.

08:42.990 --> 08:44.958
HE SAID HE'D BEEN SEEING
HIS OLD FRIENDS FROM K-TOWN,

08:44.992 --> 08:46.459
WHERE HE USED TO SCORE.

08:46.493 --> 08:49.697
I-I WAS SCARED THAT HE MIGHT BE
GOING BACK TO DRUGS.

08:49.730 --> 08:53.300
DID HE MENTION ANY OF THESE
OLD FRIENDS BY NAME?

08:53.333 --> 08:54.968
NO.

08:55.002 --> 08:56.203
SHANE.

08:56.236 --> 08:58.205
[ SIGHS ]
SHANE FLANNERY.

08:58.238 --> 09:00.040
UM [CLEARS THROAT]
HE USED TO LIVE HERE.

09:00.073 --> 09:02.776
WELL, TURNED OUT,
HE WAS KIND OF A FANATIC.

09:02.810 --> 09:06.046
HE DIDN'T THINK WE WERE DOING
ENOUGH TO PROTECT KYLE.

09:06.079 --> 09:09.650
HE THOUGHT WE WERE LETTING IN
THE SCUM OF THE EARTH --

09:09.683 --> 09:11.451
ADDICTS AND PROSTITUTES
AND ALL KINDS OF SINNERS.

09:11.484 --> 09:13.320
THAT'S WHO COMES
IN NEED OF GOD'S HEALING.

09:13.353 --> 09:15.589
SHANE THREATENED TO BURN US
ALL ALIVE IN THE HOUSE.

09:15.623 --> 09:17.658
JARED ASKED HIM TO LEAVE,
AND WHEN HE REFUSED,

09:17.691 --> 09:19.993
JARED THREW HIM OUT.

09:20.027 --> 09:21.361
YEAH, AND WHEN HE LEFT,

09:21.394 --> 09:23.997
HE WAS RANTING ABOUT JARED
PAYING FOR HIS SINS.

09:24.031 --> 09:26.734
OKAY. WELL,
WE'LL CERTAINLY LOOK INTO IT.

09:26.767 --> 09:29.169
JARED BAKER SIGNED OVER
HIS ENTIRE TRUST FUND TO YOU.

09:29.202 --> 09:30.503
HALF A MILLION DOLLARS.

09:30.537 --> 09:32.239
WHAT'D YOU DO
WITH THE MONEY?

09:32.272 --> 09:34.107
EVERYTHING WE TAKE IN
GOES TO THE SHELTER,

09:34.141 --> 09:36.076
THE FOOD BANK,
OR THE SCHOOL IN AFGHANISTAN.

09:36.109 --> 09:39.747
DID JARED EVER QUESTION HOW YOU
WERE SPENDING HIS INHERITANCE?

09:39.780 --> 09:41.481
I-I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE INSINUATING.

09:41.514 --> 09:43.751
IF YOU'RE IMPLYING THAT WE HAD
SOMETHING TO DO WITH --

09:43.784 --> 09:46.419
TOM, IT'S OKAY.

09:46.453 --> 09:47.821
PEOPLE GIVE US THEIR MONEY

09:47.855 --> 09:50.090
BECAUSE OF THE FIRST THING
GOD EVER SAID TO ME.

09:50.123 --> 09:53.994
"I ONLY ASK FOR ONE THING --
EVERYTHING.

09:54.027 --> 09:57.130
BUT IN EXCHANGE,
I GIVE EVERYTHING."

09:57.164 --> 09:59.532
Nikki:
I CAME HERE WITH NOTHING --

09:59.566 --> 10:01.534
JUST A COKE HABIT
AND A LOT OF FEAR --

10:01.568 --> 10:04.938
AND THESE PEOPLE TOOK ME IN
LIKE A DAUGHTER.

10:04.972 --> 10:07.040
AND GOD KEPT HIS PROMISE.

10:07.074 --> 10:09.209
HE GAVE ME EVERYTHING.

10:09.242 --> 10:12.545
EVEN THE MAN
THAT I'M GOING TO MARRY.

10:12.579 --> 10:14.547
Tom: YOU NEED TO
FIND SHANE FLANNERY.

10:14.581 --> 10:17.751
IF HE DID KILL JARED BAKER,
HE MIGHT KILL SOMEBODY ELSE.

10:23.757 --> 10:25.726
Kate: YES.
SHANE FLANNERY.

10:25.759 --> 10:27.895
UH-HUH. I'M E-MAILING A PHOTO
AND A DESCRIPTION.

10:27.928 --> 10:30.230
I WANT EVERY MAN ON IT
WE CAN SPARE.

10:30.263 --> 10:32.065
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

10:32.099 --> 10:34.567
I'M GONNA STICK AROUND.
I WANT TO TALK TO KYLE.

10:34.601 --> 10:36.904
ABOUT WHAT?

10:36.937 --> 10:39.306
I'M JUST CURIOUS
ABOUT SOMETHING.

10:42.609 --> 10:44.044
KYLE?

10:44.077 --> 10:45.746
DO YOU HAVE A MINUTE?

10:45.779 --> 10:49.649
SURE.

10:51.518 --> 10:54.054
HOW DID YOU KNOW
THAT I WAS A NONBELIEVER?

10:54.087 --> 10:55.823
DID, UH,
GOD TELL YOU THAT?

10:55.856 --> 10:57.324
[ CHUCKLES ]

10:57.357 --> 10:59.893
I COULD JUST SEE IT
IN YOUR FACE.

10:59.927 --> 11:03.697
IT TAKES WORK NOT TO BELIEVE
IN GOD, AND THE EFFORT SHOWS.

11:03.731 --> 11:05.298
I THINK IT TAKES
A LOT MORE EFFORT

11:05.332 --> 11:07.100
TO BELIEVE IN SOMETHING
YOU CAN'T SEE.

11:07.134 --> 11:08.335
ARE YOU KIDDING?

11:13.941 --> 11:16.910
HOW COULD ANYBODY LOOK
AT SOMETHING SO PERFECT

11:16.944 --> 11:18.178
AND BEAUTIFUL AND DELICIOUS

11:18.211 --> 11:20.447
AND THINK THAT IT GOT THAT WAY
BY ACCIDENT?

11:20.480 --> 11:22.282
WELL, THERE'S A SCIENTIFIC
ANSWER TO THAT, KYLE.

11:22.315 --> 11:23.650
EARLIER VERSIONS
OF THE RASPBERRY

11:23.683 --> 11:25.085
WEREN'T SO BEAUTIFUL
AND DELICIOUS,

11:25.118 --> 11:26.820
SO THEY COULDN'T ATTRACT
ENOUGH BIRDS

11:26.854 --> 11:29.022
TO SPREAD THEIR SEEDS
AROUND.

11:29.056 --> 11:32.025
I KNOW HOW EVOLUTION WORKS.
I LOVE DARWIN.

11:32.059 --> 11:33.794
HE WAS THE FIRST PERSON
IN HISTORY

11:33.827 --> 11:35.228
TO LOOK BEHIND THE CURTAIN

11:35.262 --> 11:37.697
AND SEE HOW GOD
ACTUALLY MAKES IT ALL WORK.

11:39.332 --> 11:43.470
WHEN DID GOD
FIRST START TALKING TO YOU?

11:43.503 --> 11:46.974
[ CHUCKLES ]
WHEN I WAS 12.

11:47.007 --> 11:48.441
BUT YOU'RE NOT FOOLING ME.

11:48.475 --> 11:49.877
I KNOW YOU THINK
I'M EITHER TOTALLY FULL OF IT

11:49.910 --> 11:51.544
OR JUST PLAIN CRAZY.

11:51.578 --> 11:53.646
AND SO DID MY PARENTS,
AT FIRST.

11:53.680 --> 11:58.185
W-WHAT DOES IT FEEL LIKE WHEN
YOU'RE HEARING GOD'S VOICE?

12:00.253 --> 12:02.890
IT'S BEAUTIFUL.

12:02.923 --> 12:04.825
EVERYTHING
KIND OF DISAPPEARS.

12:04.858 --> 12:07.761
IT'S LIKE I'M ASLEEP AND AWAKE
AT THE SAME TIME.

12:07.795 --> 12:10.197
DO YOU GET HEADACHES
WHEN THAT HAPPENS?

12:10.230 --> 12:11.231
FEEL NAUSEATED?

12:11.264 --> 12:12.499
YEAH.
HOW DID YOU KNOW?

12:12.532 --> 12:15.468
JUST A HUNCH.

12:15.502 --> 12:18.138
WELL, ANYWAY,
IT'S TOTALLY WORTH IT

12:18.171 --> 12:21.975
'CAUSE I ALSO GET THIS AMAZING,
LIKE, EUPHORIA.

12:22.009 --> 12:23.643
HMM.

12:23.676 --> 12:27.147
HEADACHES, NAUSEA,
EUPHORIA, VOICES --

12:27.180 --> 12:30.683
THESE ARE CLASSIC SYMPTOMS
OF TEMPORAL LOBE EPILEPSY,

12:30.717 --> 12:32.085
WHICH COULD BE CAUSED
BY A TUMOR.

12:32.119 --> 12:33.420
I-I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

12:33.453 --> 12:35.255
HE HAS A CHECK-UP
EVERY YEAR,

12:35.288 --> 12:36.990
AND HIS DOCTOR
HAS NEVER SAID ANYTHING.

12:37.024 --> 12:38.691
DID YOU EVER TAKE HIM
TO A NEUROLOGIST?

12:38.725 --> 12:40.527
THERE WAS NO REASON TO.
HE'S IN PERFECT HEALTH.

12:40.560 --> 12:43.163
I'M SORRY, BUT HE'S NOT.

12:43.196 --> 12:44.697
THIS KIND OF TUMOR

12:44.731 --> 12:46.433
CAN ALSO PRESS ON NEIGHBORING
AREAS OF THE BRAIN.

12:46.466 --> 12:49.202
IT CAN BE LIFE-THREATENING
IF IT'S NOT TREATED,

12:49.236 --> 12:51.204
OF KYLE COULD HAVE A SEIZURE
WHILE HE'S DRIVING.

12:51.238 --> 12:52.772
I'D LIKE TO BRING HIM IN
FOR SOME TESTS.

12:52.806 --> 12:54.507
AND IF THEY SHOW
WHAT I THINK THEY'LL SHOW,

12:54.541 --> 12:55.909
HE MAY NEED SURGERY.

12:55.943 --> 12:57.777
WELL, I-I COULD BRING HIM IN
TOMORROW WHEN --

12:57.811 --> 12:59.012
Kyle: MOM, WAIT.

12:59.046 --> 13:01.181
ARE YOU SAYING THIS CONDITION

13:01.214 --> 13:03.383
IS WHAT'S MAKING ME
HEAR GOD'S VOICE?

13:03.416 --> 13:05.718
IT'S NOT GOD, KYLE.

13:05.752 --> 13:07.554
IT'S A NEUROLOGICAL
ABNORMALITY.

13:07.587 --> 13:09.722
WELL, IF IT IS,
GOD MUST HAVE GIVEN IT TO ME

13:09.756 --> 13:11.224
SO HE COULD HAVE A WAY
TO TALK TO ME.

13:11.258 --> 13:12.392
I'M NOT GETTING RID OF IT.

13:12.425 --> 13:15.128
THIS COULD BE
A FATAL CONDITION.

13:15.162 --> 13:16.729
BEING ALIVE
IS A FATAL CONDITION.

13:16.763 --> 13:18.698
I'M NOT DOING IT, MOM.

13:18.731 --> 13:21.701
MRS. SHELBY, I UNDERSTAND KYLE'S
COMMITMENT TO HIS BELIEFS,

13:21.734 --> 13:23.070
BUT HE IS STILL A MINOR.

13:23.103 --> 13:25.138
YOU CAN COMPEL HIM
TO GET TREATMENT.

13:25.172 --> 13:27.407
DR. PIERCE, WE'LL DISCUSS
WHAT YOU'VE SAID.

13:27.440 --> 13:29.209
WE'LL TALK TO KYLE
ABOUT IT.

13:29.242 --> 13:31.744
BUT WE ARE NOT GONNA FORCE HIM
TO DO ANYTHING AGAINST HIS WILL.

13:44.791 --> 13:46.426
Daniel:
THIS IS CHILD ABUSE!

13:46.459 --> 13:47.928
THEY'RE NOT FORCING HIM
TO GET TESTED

13:47.961 --> 13:49.129
BECAUSE THEY DON'T WANT
THE GOOSE

13:49.162 --> 13:50.730
TO STOP LAYING
THE GOLDEN EGGS.

13:50.763 --> 13:52.365
[ Chuckling ] IT'S WHAT I'VE
ALWAYS SAID -- RELIGION.

13:52.399 --> 13:54.334
AND, YOU KNOW, IF IT'S NOT
ABOUT BLOOD OR OPPRESSION,

13:54.367 --> 13:56.003
IT'S ABOUT MONEY
IN THE BANK.

13:56.036 --> 13:58.338
THAT IS A GROSS
GENERALIZATION,

13:58.371 --> 14:00.673
NOT TO MENTION
TOTALLY OFFENSIVE.

14:00.707 --> 14:03.176
I MEAN, WHAT ABOUT
THE DALAI LAMA OR --

14:03.210 --> 14:04.677
OR MARTIN LUTHER KING?

14:04.711 --> 14:07.680
OR THE INQUISITION
OR 9/11 OR GIORDANO BRUNO?

14:07.714 --> 14:10.350
OH, THEY DIDN'T TEACH YOU
ABOUT HIM IN SUNDAY SCHOOL?

14:10.383 --> 14:14.021
1592 -- GIORDANO BRUNO
MAKES THE WILD, SATANIC CLAIM

14:14.054 --> 14:15.855
THAT THE EARTH
REVOLVES AROUND THE SUN,

14:15.889 --> 14:17.690
SO THE HOLY FATHERS
PRAY TO GOD

14:17.724 --> 14:19.526
AND ARE TOLD THAT
THIS WICKED MAN MUST DIE.

14:19.559 --> 14:22.529
THEY CLAMP HIS TONGUE
TO THE ROOF OF HIS MOUTH,

14:22.562 --> 14:23.830
AND THEY BURN HIM ALIVE,

14:23.863 --> 14:24.965
WHICH MUST HAVE BEEN
THE RIGHT THING TO DO

14:24.998 --> 14:26.299
'CAUSE GOD TOLD THEM
TO DO IT.

14:26.333 --> 14:28.268
LOOK, YES,
THAT IS A HORRIBLE STORY,

14:28.301 --> 14:30.637
BUT HAVEN HOUSE
ISN'T BURNING PEOPLE ALIVE.

14:30.670 --> 14:32.372
YOU MADE A SNAP DIAGNOSIS

14:32.405 --> 14:34.207
AFTER TALKING TO THAT KID
FOR FIVE MINUTES.

14:34.241 --> 14:35.909
YOU DON'T THINK THAT
THAT MIGHT BE

14:35.943 --> 14:37.844
YOUR PREJUDICE
AGAINST RELIGION TALKING?

14:37.877 --> 14:39.846
I-I DIDN'T MAKE
THE CONDITION UP.

14:39.879 --> 14:41.514
IT'S WHAT
JOAN WHAT?C HAD.

14:41.548 --> 14:43.683
JOAN OF ARC HAD
TEMPORAL LOBE EPILEPSY.

14:43.716 --> 14:46.019
IT'S WHY SHE THOUGHT
THAT ANGELS WERE TALKING TO HER.

14:46.053 --> 14:47.854
OH, DID YOU EXAMINE HER,
TOO?

14:47.887 --> 14:49.923
IT'S THE CONCLUSION
OF MEDICAL HISTORIANS

14:49.957 --> 14:52.125
BASED ON HER DESCRIPTION
OF HER OWN EXPERIENCE.

14:52.159 --> 14:53.826
AND WE ALL KNOW
WHAT HAPPENED TO HER.

14:53.860 --> 14:56.796
YES. SHE BECAME A GREAT LEADER.
SHE LIBERATED FRANCE.

14:56.829 --> 14:59.066
SHE WAS BURNED AT THE STAKE
AT AGE 19.

14:59.099 --> 15:02.569
SHE WAS A DELUDED GIRL WHOSE
ILLNESS LED TO HER DISASTER.

15:02.602 --> 15:04.304
SHE WAS A HERO.

15:04.337 --> 15:07.240
AT A TIME WHEN WOMEN HAD
LESS POWER THAN FARM ANIMALS,

15:07.274 --> 15:08.741
SHE LED AN ARMY.

15:08.775 --> 15:10.377
I USED TO CARRY HER MEDAL
WHEN I WAS A KID,

15:10.410 --> 15:13.146
AND I STILL LIGHT CANDLES
IN CHURCH FOR HER ON SUNDAY.

15:13.180 --> 15:15.148
YOUYES, DANIEL, I DO.H?

15:15.182 --> 15:17.317
AND I PRAY, TOO,
IF YOU WANT TO KNOW.

15:17.350 --> 15:18.418
WHY?

15:18.451 --> 15:20.320
BECAUSE I BELIEVE
IN GOD.

15:20.353 --> 15:22.655
IT COMFORTS ME TO TALK TO HIM
ABOUT MY PROBLEMS.

15:22.689 --> 15:25.325
AND DOES HE ANSWER YOU BACK
LIKE HE DOES WITH KYLE?

15:25.358 --> 15:26.960
OKAY.
YOU KNOW WHAT?

15:26.994 --> 15:29.162
I DO NOT HAVE TIME TO GET INTO
A THEOLOGICAL DEBATE WITH YOU.

15:29.196 --> 15:30.730
I NEED TO FIND
SHANE FLANNERY.

15:30.763 --> 15:32.765
WHICH IS EXACTLY WHAT
OUR FRIENDS AT HAVEN HOUSE

15:32.799 --> 15:34.034
WANT YOU TO BE DOING.

15:34.067 --> 15:36.036
HOW DO YOU KNOW
THAT JARED BAKER

15:36.069 --> 15:37.770
DIDN'T JUST GET
[BLEEP] OFF ONE DAY

15:37.804 --> 15:39.839
THAT HIS ENTIRE TRUST FUND
WAS GOING INTO THEIR POCKETS,

15:39.872 --> 15:42.042
SO HE TRIED TO GET IT BACK,
AND THEY OFFED HIM FOR IT?

15:42.075 --> 15:44.611
BECAUSE THE I.R.S.
IS ALL OVER PLACES LIKE THAT.

15:44.644 --> 15:46.379
OH, AND NOTHING
EVER GETS PAST UNCLE SAM.

15:46.413 --> 15:48.848
ALL RIGHT, FINE, IF IT WOULD
MAKE YOU FEEL BETTER,

15:48.881 --> 15:50.683
I WILL PUT IN A CALL
TO THE I.R.S.,

15:50.717 --> 15:52.719
BUT MY MONEY IS ON SHANE.

15:56.923 --> 15:59.126
Ethan: I WAS EXACTLY
WHERE YOU ARE, DR. PIERCE.

15:59.159 --> 16:01.094
I WAS POSITIVE A PLACE RAKING IN
THAT KIND OF CASH

16:01.128 --> 16:02.762
HAD TO BE A SCAM,

16:02.795 --> 16:04.397
BUT I'VE BEEN TEARING
THEIR BOOKS APART AT THE SEAMS

16:04.431 --> 16:06.399
FOR TWO YEARS, AND I GOT TO
TELL YOU, IT'S LEGIT.

16:06.433 --> 16:07.900
WE'RE TALKING
ABOUT MILLIONS OF DOLLARS.

16:07.934 --> 16:09.402
WHERE IS IT ALL GOING?

16:09.436 --> 16:11.404
WELL, ABOUT 2% GOES
TO ADMINISTRATIVE EXPENSES,

16:11.438 --> 16:13.506
WHICH IS AS LOW AS IT GETS
IN NONPROFIT-LAND,

16:13.540 --> 16:15.708
AND SOME GOES
TO LOCAL CHARITIES --

16:15.742 --> 16:17.910
FOOD BANK, MEALS ON WHEELS,
SHELTER.

16:17.944 --> 16:20.313
BIGGEST CHUNK GOES
TO THE SCHOOL IN AFGHANISTAN.

16:20.347 --> 16:21.614
[ CELLMORETTI.NGS ]

16:21.648 --> 16:22.982
ISN'T IT POSSIBLE
THEY'RE FOOLING YOU?

16:23.016 --> 16:24.484
THAT -- THAT
THEY'RE COOKING THE BOOKS?

16:24.517 --> 16:26.753
I'D LIKE TO THINK,
AFTER 20 YEARS IN THIS PLACE,

16:26.786 --> 16:28.255
THAT I'M A PRETTY HARD GUY
TO FOOL.

16:28.288 --> 16:29.289
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

16:29.322 --> 16:31.924
CPD JUST FOUND
OUR SUSPECT.

16:31.958 --> 16:34.427
THANK YOU.

16:34.461 --> 16:36.096
Kate: MR. FLANNERY,

16:36.129 --> 16:38.765
DID YOU THREATEN
TO BURN DOWN HAVEN HOUSE,

16:38.798 --> 16:40.433
SEND ALL ITS RESIDENTS
TO HELL?

16:40.467 --> 16:42.235
I SPOKE THE TRUTH.

16:42.269 --> 16:45.438
I SAID THAT GOD WOULD BRING
THE FIRE OF HIS VENGEANCE

16:45.472 --> 16:47.407
DOWN ON THAT HOUSE.

16:47.440 --> 16:50.243
DID YOU SPECIFICALLY THREATEN
TO KILL JARED BAKER?

16:50.277 --> 16:53.513
IT WAS GOD WHO DELIVERED
HIS JUDGMENT ON THAT HERETIC.

16:53.546 --> 16:55.615
OKAY. WHERE WERE YOU
LAST TUESDAY MORNING?

16:55.648 --> 16:57.184
ACROSS THE STREET
FROM HAVEN HOUSE,

16:57.217 --> 16:58.951
GUARDING THE CHOSEN ONE --
I WAS THERE ALL NIGHT.

16:58.985 --> 17:00.687
CAN ANYONE VERIFY THAT?

17:00.720 --> 17:03.923
ONLY GOD, WHO WILL PURIFY
ALL THE SINNERS IN THAT HOUSE

17:03.956 --> 17:05.958
WITH THE FIRES
OF HIS VENGEANCE...

17:05.992 --> 17:09.529
STARTING WITH THOSE WHO TRAMPLE
ON THE SEVENTH COMMANDMENT.

17:09.562 --> 17:11.831
OKAY, I'M A LITTLE RUSTY
ON MY COMMANDMENTS,

17:11.864 --> 17:14.334
BUT I THINK I REMEMBER
WHICH ONE THE SEVENTH IS.

17:14.367 --> 17:16.769
NOW, WHO IN THE HOUSE
WAS COMMITTING ADULTERY?

17:16.803 --> 17:18.605
THAT LYING [BLEEP]
NIKKI.

17:19.572 --> 17:21.474
SHE'S ENGAGED
TO KYLE'S BROTHER,

17:21.508 --> 17:24.711
SO WHY WAS SHE RUTTING
LIKE A SOW WITH THE DEAD MAN?

17:24.744 --> 17:26.646
OKAY, SO, YOU'RE SAYING

17:26.679 --> 17:30.483
NIKKI WAS RUTTING LIKE A SOW
WITH JARED BAKER?

17:30.517 --> 17:32.319
IT WAS AFTER MIDNIGHT.

17:32.352 --> 17:34.587
I SAW THE LIGHT GO ON
IN HIS WINDOW.

17:34.621 --> 17:38.057
SHE CAME INTO HIS ROOM
AND TOOK HIM IN HER ARMS.

17:38.091 --> 17:40.893
MAYBE KYLE'S BROTHER
SAW WHAT I SAW.

17:40.927 --> 17:44.164
MAYBE GOD ENTRUSTED HIM
WITH THE FIRE OF HIS VENGEANCE.

17:44.197 --> 17:46.533
[ French accent ]
HE IS NOT THE KILLER.

17:49.001 --> 17:50.603
HAVE YOU EVER MET
A HOLY WARRIOR

17:50.637 --> 17:52.672
WHO SHOT HIS VICTIM
IN THE BACK?

17:52.705 --> 17:55.508
NORMALLY, THEY BURN
THEIR VICTIMS OR CRUCIFY THEM

17:55.542 --> 17:57.510
OR RITUALLY DRAIN
THEIR BLOOD.

17:57.544 --> 18:00.313
SHE'S CHASING
THE WRONG CAT.

18:00.347 --> 18:03.850
I WAS SENT TO HELP YOU
CATCH THE RIGHT ONE.

18:03.883 --> 18:06.753
WHAT DO YOU MEAN, "SENT"?
WHO SENT YOU?

18:06.786 --> 18:08.655
GOD, OF COURSE.

18:10.557 --> 18:13.193
MESSENGER OF GOD.

18:13.226 --> 18:14.861
FRENCH ACCENT.

18:14.894 --> 18:17.096
LATE MEDIEVAL,
HOMESPUN TUNIC.

18:17.130 --> 18:19.031
GREAT.

18:19.065 --> 18:21.534
I'M HALLUCINATING
JOAN OF ARC.

18:21.568 --> 18:23.436
ENCHANTé.

18:31.311 --> 18:33.946
EVIL IS IN THE EYE
OF THE BEHOLDER,

18:33.980 --> 18:35.715
ESPECIALLY IF THAT BEHOLDER
IS SHANE FLANNERY.

18:35.748 --> 18:38.285
SO, YOU ADMIT THAT YOU WERE
IN JARED'S ROOM THAT NIGHT?

18:38.318 --> 18:41.454
YES, BUT NOT FOR ANYTHING
SINFUL.

18:41.488 --> 18:43.122
JARED NEEDED MY HELP.

18:43.156 --> 18:44.424
AT 2:00 IN THE MORNING?

18:44.457 --> 18:46.226
MY ROOM IS
RIGHT NEXT DOOR TO HIS.

18:46.259 --> 18:47.927
I WOKE UP.
I HEARD HIM CRYING.

18:47.960 --> 18:50.463
I WAS WORRIED, SO I WENT
AND KNOCKED ON HIS DOOR.

18:50.497 --> 18:51.864
DO YOU THINK
THAT YOUR FIANCé

18:51.898 --> 18:53.600
MIGHT HAVE SEEN YOU
KNOCK ON HIS DOOR?

18:53.633 --> 18:56.369
NO. GREG -- GREG'S ROOM
IS DOWNSTAIRS IN THE BACK.

18:56.403 --> 18:58.871
JARED WAS
IN A TERRIBLE STATE.

18:58.905 --> 19:01.541
HE TOLD ME HE HAD BEEN
SEEING HIS FRIENDS IN K-TOWN

19:01.574 --> 19:03.643
AND THAT HE WAS WORRIED
HE MIGHT SLIP.

19:03.676 --> 19:07.146
SO WE PRAYED TOGETHER.
I HELD HIM.

19:07.180 --> 19:09.982
HE READ THAT THE WRONG WAY
AND MADE A PASS AT ME.

19:10.016 --> 19:11.484
I TOLD HIM
I WOULD NEVER BETRAY GREG,

19:11.518 --> 19:12.952
AND I WENT BACK
TO MY ROOM.

19:12.985 --> 19:15.655
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL US
ANY OF THIS BEFORE?

19:15.688 --> 19:18.325
I TOLD YOU THAT I THOUGHT
JARED WAS HAVING A ROUGH TIME.

19:18.358 --> 19:22.629
I DIDN'T TELL YOU THE REST
BECAUSE GREG LOVED JARED.

19:22.662 --> 19:25.665
IT WOULD HAVE ONLY UPSET HIM,
AND FOR WHAT?

19:31.037 --> 19:34.173
HEY.
I HEARD YOU GUYS WERE BACK.

19:34.207 --> 19:35.842
DID YKate: YES.ANE?

19:35.875 --> 19:37.677
BUT WE DON'T THINK
HDANIEL.T.

19:39.045 --> 19:42.181
WE'RE NOT REALLY SUPPOSED TO
DISCUSS AN OPEN INVESTIGATION.

19:42.215 --> 19:45.585
WELL, WHAT WERE YOU
TALKING TO NIKKI ABOUT?

19:45.618 --> 19:47.086
DOES SHE KNOW
SOMETHING?

19:47.119 --> 19:48.321
KYLE, I --

19:48.355 --> 19:49.789
OKAY.

19:49.822 --> 19:53.092
DR. PIERCE, CAN I TALK
TO YOU FOR A MINUTE?

19:53.125 --> 19:54.494
NOT ABOUT THE CASE.

19:54.527 --> 19:56.863
I'LL BE IN THE CAR.

19:58.865 --> 20:01.200
WHAT'S ON YOUR MIND?

20:04.637 --> 20:06.038
A WHILE AGO,

20:06.072 --> 20:08.641
GOD TOLD ME I WASN'T
GONNA BE ALIVE FOR VERY LONG.

20:10.042 --> 20:12.945
I GUESS HE'S SAYING
THE SAME THING YOU ARE.

20:12.979 --> 20:15.615
YOU KNOW I DON'T BELIEVE
IN GOD, KYLE.

20:15.648 --> 20:18.318
BUT IF A GUT INSTINCT IS
TELLING YOU YOU'RE NOT WELL,

20:18.351 --> 20:20.520
YOU SHOULD LISTEN TO IT
AND GET TREATMENT.

20:20.553 --> 20:22.622
I'M NOT DOING THAT.

20:22.655 --> 20:25.057
I JUST WANT TO KNOW
HOW LONG I HAVE

20:25.091 --> 20:28.628
SO I CAN,
YOU KNOW, MAKE PLANS.

20:28.661 --> 20:30.763
YOUR CONDITION
ISN'T ALWAYS FATAL.

20:32.299 --> 20:34.967
AND THERE'S NO WAY TO PREDICT
HOW LONG IT'LL TAKE

20:35.001 --> 20:37.136
ANY ILLNESS
TO CAUSE SOMEONE'S DEATH.

20:37.169 --> 20:39.572
SO, SCIENCE DOESN'T HAVE
ALL THE ANSWERS?

20:39.606 --> 20:41.974
I SUPPOSE NOT.

20:42.008 --> 20:44.644
THAT'S OKAY.

20:44.677 --> 20:46.279
NEITHER DOES GOD.

20:46.313 --> 20:48.681
HE SPENDS MOST OF HIS TIME
TRYING TO FIGURE OUT

20:48.715 --> 20:50.483
WHY WE DO
THE CRAZY THINGS WE DO.

20:50.517 --> 20:53.920
THAT'S WHY HE MADE
BRAIN SCIENTISTS LIKE YOU --

20:53.953 --> 20:55.655
TO HELP HIM
FIGURE IT ALL OUT.

20:55.688 --> 20:57.056
HEY.
SORRY TO INTERRUPT.

20:57.089 --> 20:58.257
I NEED TO GET BACK
TO THE OFFICE.

20:58.291 --> 20:59.592
WHAT'S GOING ON?

20:59.626 --> 21:02.228
CPD found a witness
in K-Town

21:02.261 --> 21:06.165
who said they saw a guy roughing
up Jared Baker a few days ago.

21:06.198 --> 21:07.300
We're looking for him now.

21:07.334 --> 21:08.901
LISTEN, UM...

21:08.935 --> 21:10.603
CALL ME ANYTIME

21:10.637 --> 21:13.806
ABOUT YOUR HEALTH
OR JUST TO TALK.

21:13.840 --> 21:16.309
THANKS.
I'LL DO THAT.

21:16.343 --> 21:18.010
[ BACH'S "PARTITA NO. 6
IN E MINOR" PLAYS ]

21:18.044 --> 21:21.013
Daniel: HOW COULD SUCH
AN INTELLIGENT, LEVEL-HEADED KID

21:21.047 --> 21:22.815
BE SO MEDIEVAL AT HEART?

21:22.849 --> 21:25.017
NOT TO MENTION KATE.

21:25.051 --> 21:28.187
DANIEL, THAT MAN
WHO'S MUSIC YOU'RE PLAYING

21:28.220 --> 21:29.822
WAS A DEVOUT BELIEVER.

21:29.856 --> 21:33.326
BACH LIVED 300 YEARS AGO.
SCIENCE WAS IN THE CRADLE.

21:33.360 --> 21:35.828
ISN'T SCIENCE
JUST ANOTHER KIND OF FAITH

21:35.862 --> 21:38.030
WITH ITS OWN SCRIPTURES
AND ITS OWN DOGMAS?

21:38.064 --> 21:40.032
SCIENCE IS BASED ON FACT.

21:40.066 --> 21:42.602
IT MUST BE EXHAUSTING
TO BE SO CYNICAL ALL THE TIME.

21:42.635 --> 21:45.772
IT'S NOT CYNICISM --
IT'S REALITY.

21:45.805 --> 21:49.342
AND, OF COURSE, WE ALL KNOW WHAT
A FIRM GRIP YOU HAVE ON REALITY.

21:49.376 --> 21:51.478
OH, THAT'S VERY FUNNY.

21:51.511 --> 21:53.079
I THINK YOU'RE JEALOUS
OF PEOPLE WITH FAITH.

21:53.112 --> 21:55.548
YOU WISH YOU COULD FIND
THAT KIND OF SOLACE AND COMFORT.

21:55.582 --> 21:56.983
[ MUSIC RESUMES ]

21:57.016 --> 21:58.985
LISTEN TO THAT TREBLE.]

21:59.018 --> 22:01.854
HMM? LIKE A CHICKEN
SCREAMING FOR ITS LIFE.

22:01.888 --> 22:05.558
I'VE SEEN YOU LOOKING LONGINGLY
AT A SATIN-FINISH EBONY GRAND

22:05.592 --> 22:07.560
IN THE STEINWAY SHOWROOM
DOWNTOWN.

22:07.594 --> 22:10.363
YEAH, WELL, THAT PARTICULAR
SATIN-FINISH EBONY GRAND

22:10.397 --> 22:12.064
COSTS AS MUCH
AS MOST CARS.

22:12.098 --> 22:14.867
DANIEL, YOU JUST GOT A CHECK
FOR $50,000.

22:14.901 --> 22:17.370
YOU CAN BUY ANYTHING
YOU WANT WITH IT.

22:17.404 --> 22:19.739
THAT WOULD BE
AN INSANE INDULGENCE.

22:19.772 --> 22:21.808
YOU'VE DONE
CRAZIER THINGS.

22:21.841 --> 22:24.243
YOU REALLY THINK
I SHOULD BUY IT?

22:24.276 --> 22:27.246
HEY, DOC. KYLE JENSEN'S MOTHER
IS ON THE PHONE.

22:27.279 --> 22:28.848
SHE SOUNDS PRETTY UPSET.

22:31.551 --> 22:34.754
Sandy: [ Voice breaking ]
KYLE RUNS UP AND DOWN THOSE
STAIRS 20 TIMES A DAY.

22:34.787 --> 22:37.890
HE MUST HAVE GONE INTO ONE
OF HIS TRANCES AN[ SIGHS ]

22:37.924 --> 22:39.859
WHY WOULD GOD CHOOSE
A MOMENT LIKE THAT?

22:39.892 --> 22:42.028
Dr. Goldsby:
MR. AND MRS. SHELBY,

22:42.061 --> 22:44.497
KYLE SUFFERED A MAJOR
HEAD TRAUMA IN THE FALL,

22:44.531 --> 22:46.899
CAUSING HIS BRAIN
TO BLEED.

22:46.933 --> 22:48.901
IN A WAY, THE FALL
MAY HAVE BEEN FORTUNATE

22:48.935 --> 22:50.603
BECAUSE THE SCAN
REVEALED SOMETHING

22:50.637 --> 22:52.905
WE MIGHT NOT HAVE CAUGHT
UNTIL IT WAS TOO LATE.

22:52.939 --> 22:57.410
KYLE HAS AN INVASIVE TUMOR
IN HIS LEFT TEMPORAL LOBE.

22:57.444 --> 22:59.712
IT'S POSSIBLE THE FALL
DISLODGED IT,

22:59.746 --> 23:01.814
WHICH IS WHAT'S CAUSING
THE SEVERE BLEEDING.

23:03.049 --> 23:04.517
LORD IN HEAVEN.

23:04.551 --> 23:05.718
[ SIGHS ] THAT'S WHAT
YOU TOLD US YESTERDAY.

23:05.752 --> 23:07.787
WE SHOULD HAVE
LISTENED TO YOU.

23:07.820 --> 23:09.522
WE SHOULD HAVE -- WE SHOULD HAVE
BROUGHT HIM IN FOR TESTS.

23:09.556 --> 23:11.290
I NEED TO OPERATE
IMMEDIATELY

23:11.323 --> 23:13.426
TO RELIEVE THE PRESSURE
FROM THE BLEEDING.

23:13.460 --> 23:16.028
IF WE CAN REMOVE THE TUMOR,
WE WILL.

23:16.062 --> 23:18.197
KYLE MADE IT CLEAR THAT
HE DIDN'T WANT TO DO ANYTHING

23:18.230 --> 23:19.999
THAT MIGHT CUT HIM OFF
FROM GOD.

23:20.032 --> 23:22.902
YOU CAN'T LEAVE A DISLODGED
TUMOR INSIDE YOUR SON'S BRAIN.

23:22.935 --> 23:24.804
I'M JUST THINKING
OF WHAT KYLE WOULD WANT.

23:24.837 --> 23:26.138
YOU MIGHT AS WELL
SHOOT HIM IN THE HEAD!

23:26.172 --> 23:27.173
DANIEL.

23:27.206 --> 23:28.675
Sandy:
DR. PIERCE IS RIGHT.

23:28.708 --> 23:32.378
[ Crying ] I KNOW KYLE
MAY BE ANGRY WITH ME,

23:32.411 --> 23:36.583
BUT I AM NOT GOING TO
LOSE MY SON.

23:36.616 --> 23:38.050
WE'LL PREP HIM
FOR SURGERY.

23:39.852 --> 23:42.421
DOCTOR, DID --

23:42.455 --> 23:44.657
DID KYLE HAVE ELEVATED PROLACTIN
LEVELS WHEN HE CAME IN?

23:44.691 --> 23:47.326
NO. THEY WERE NORMAL,
BUT NEED TO GET STARTED, SO...

23:47.359 --> 23:49.562
WHAT WAS THAT ABOUT?

23:49.596 --> 23:52.899
ELEVATED PROLACTIN WOULD MEAN
THAT KYLE HAD A SEIZURE

23:52.932 --> 23:54.834
IN THE LAST COUPLE OF HOURS,
BUT HE DIDN'T.

23:54.867 --> 23:57.336
SO HE DIDN'T FALL
BECAUSE HE WENT INTO A TRANCE.

23:57.369 --> 23:59.572
MAYBE HE FIGURED OUT
WHO KILLED JARED.

23:59.606 --> 24:01.107
AND SOMEONE PUSHED HIM.

24:13.252 --> 24:15.622
Kate: DID ANY OF YOU
SEE KYLE FALL?

24:15.655 --> 24:17.289
I WAS IN THE DEN,
READING, AND --

24:17.323 --> 24:20.960
AND, UH, HEARD A CRASH
AND RAN INTO THE FOYER.

24:20.993 --> 24:23.796
JAKE AND TINA CAME TO MY ROOM
AND TOLD ME WHAT HAPPENED.

24:23.830 --> 24:27.800
I WAS MAKING DINNER,
AND I HEARD TOM YELL FOR HELP.

24:27.834 --> 24:30.637
WHEN I SAW HIM ON THE GROUND,
ALL THAT BLOOD, I --

24:30.670 --> 24:32.138
[ CELEXCUSE ME.GS ]

24:32.171 --> 24:33.472
MORETTI.

24:33.506 --> 24:35.474
WHY'S SHE ASKING
ALL THESE QUESTIONS?

24:35.508 --> 24:37.977
NOBODY IN THE HOUSE
WOULD WANT TO HURT KYLE.

24:38.010 --> 24:39.311
ARE YOU SURE ABOUT THAT?

24:39.345 --> 24:41.047
Kate: DANIEL.

24:44.250 --> 24:45.885
THEY FOUND THE GUY WHO
BEAT UP JARED IN K-TOWN.

24:45.918 --> 24:48.020
WHAT ABOUT KYLE?

24:48.054 --> 24:49.522
WELL, THE FAMILY WILL CALL US
IF THERE'S ANY NEWS.

24:49.556 --> 24:51.724
NO, I MEAN
ABOUT PROTECTING HIM.

24:51.758 --> 24:53.526
SOMEBODY TRIED TO KILL HIM.
THEY MAY TRY AGAIN.

24:53.560 --> 24:55.161
YOU -- YOU GOT TO PUT
A GUARD ON HIM.

24:55.194 --> 24:56.896
DANIEL, I'M NOT GONNA BE ABLE
TO GET APPROVAL FOR A GUARD

24:56.929 --> 24:58.531
ON A HOSPITAL ROOM 24/7

24:58.565 --> 25:01.400
JUST BECAUSE WE HAVE
AN UNSUBSTANTIATED THEORY.

25:01.433 --> 25:03.335
[ SIGHS ]
WELL, I'M STAYING.

25:04.537 --> 25:06.372
ALL RIGHT.

25:07.774 --> 25:09.742
Aaron: ARE YOU SAYING
THAT I KILLED JARED BAKER?

25:09.776 --> 25:12.311
WITNESSES SAW YOU TWO
GET INTO A SHOVING MATCH

25:12.344 --> 25:14.313
A FEW DAYS
BEFORE HE WAS MURDERED.

25:14.346 --> 25:17.016
LOOK, I DO OUTREACH
FOR THE V.A.,

25:17.049 --> 25:18.117
AND WE GET A LOT
OF THESE VETS

25:18.150 --> 25:19.686
LIVING ON THE STREET
AROUND HERE,

25:19.719 --> 25:22.154
SO, YEAH, IT [BLEEP] ME OFF
WHEN THESE [BLEEP] COME DOWN

25:22.188 --> 25:24.657
AND TRY TO SCAM THESE GUYS
OUT OF THEIR SDI CHECKS.

25:24.691 --> 25:27.326
JARED BAKER
WAS SCAMMING VETERANS?

25:27.359 --> 25:29.328
PASSING OUT PAMPHLETS,
HAWKING SOME CHURCH

25:29.361 --> 25:31.664
THAT'S ABOUT DONATING
EVERY CENT THEY GOT,

25:31.698 --> 25:32.932
SO I TOSSED HIS PAMPHLETS

25:32.965 --> 25:34.701
AND TOLD HIM
TO TAKE HIS SCAM ELSEWHERE.

25:34.734 --> 25:37.169
AND THEN WHEN HE DIDN'T GET
THE MESSAGE, YOU GOT PHYSICAL.

25:38.871 --> 25:41.173
AFTER HE TOOK OFF, I FELT BAD
ABOUT THE WHOLE THING,

25:41.207 --> 25:43.142
SO I FISHED ONE OF THE PAMPHLETS
OUT OF THE TRASH

25:43.175 --> 25:44.276
AND TOOK A LOOK.

25:44.310 --> 25:46.278
AND GUESS WHAT --
I WAS RIGHT.

25:46.312 --> 25:47.647
IT'S ALL A BIG FAKE --

25:47.680 --> 25:49.115
AT LEAST THE SCHOOL
IN AFGHANISTAN IS.

25:50.116 --> 25:51.784
THAT PLACE
DOES NOT EXIST.

25:51.818 --> 25:54.453
HOW DO YOU KNOW THAT?

25:54.486 --> 25:55.688
PICTURE IN THE PAMPHLET.

25:55.722 --> 25:58.024
SCHOOLKIDS
IN FRONT OF A BIG LAKE?

25:58.057 --> 25:59.558
SCHOOL'S SUPPOSED TO BE
IN MAIMANA.

25:59.592 --> 26:02.795
I WAS STATIONED IN HERAT,
A STONE'S THROW FROM THERE.

26:02.829 --> 26:05.197
THERE'S NO LAKE IN THAT VALLEY,
JUST SAND.

26:05.231 --> 26:07.033
THIS PICTURE?

26:07.066 --> 26:08.534
YEAH.

26:10.269 --> 26:11.904
SEE THE WRITING
ON THE BLACKBOARD?

26:11.938 --> 26:13.105
THAT'S FARSI.

26:13.139 --> 26:14.874
IN MAIMANA,
THEY SPEAK ARABIC.

26:14.907 --> 26:16.909
I CALLED A BUNCH OF GUYS
WHO SERVED OVER THERE.

26:16.943 --> 26:18.811
NOBODY EVER HEARD
OF AN INTERNATIONAL GROUP

26:18.845 --> 26:20.579
OPERATING A SCHOOL
ANYWHERE NEAR MAIMANA.

26:20.613 --> 26:22.815
YOU REPORT THIS TO ANYONE?

26:22.849 --> 26:24.550
JUST JARED BAKER.

26:24.583 --> 26:26.819
WAIT. JARED KNEW?

26:26.853 --> 26:28.487
NEXT TIME HE CAME DOWN
TO K-TOWN,

26:28.520 --> 26:30.489
I TOLD HIM
EXACTLY WHAT I JUST TOLD YOU.

26:30.522 --> 26:31.824
HOW DID HE TAKE IT?

26:31.858 --> 26:33.492
IT SHOOK HIM UP.

26:33.525 --> 26:35.227
HE SAID HE WANTED TO REPORT IT
TO SOMEBODY,

26:35.261 --> 26:36.996
SO I TOLD HIM
HE SHOULD START WITH THE I.R.S.

26:37.029 --> 26:40.266
THE I.R.S. GAVE HAVEN HOUSE
A CLEAN BILL OF HEALTH.

26:53.980 --> 26:56.749
LAST-MINUTE VACATION,
ETHAN?

26:58.651 --> 27:01.788
WE REMOVED THE TUMOR
AND STOPPED THE BLEEDING.

27:01.821 --> 27:02.955
[ SIGHS ]

27:02.989 --> 27:06.258
BUT THERE WERE
COMPLICATIONS.

27:06.292 --> 27:07.927
KYLE SUFFERED
A RUPTURED ANEURYSM.

27:07.960 --> 27:09.261
HE'S IN A COMA.

27:09.295 --> 27:11.931
[ SOBS ]
OH, MY GOD.

27:11.964 --> 27:14.901
THE SITUATION
WIDOESN'T LOOK GOOD.?

27:17.704 --> 27:19.071
COULD HE DIE?

27:19.105 --> 27:22.108
I THINK YOU NEED TO
PREPARE YOURSELVES

27:22.141 --> 27:24.543
FOR THAT POSSIBILITY.

27:24.576 --> 27:25.644
I'M SORRY.

27:25.678 --> 27:27.146
[ CRYING ]

27:27.179 --> 27:30.316
SURE.
I'LL TAKE YOU IN.

27:42.194 --> 27:44.831
[ SIGHS ]

27:44.864 --> 27:47.199
IT IS A PITY...

27:47.233 --> 27:48.701
N'EST-CE PAS?

27:48.735 --> 27:52.471
THEY CALL YOU
"THE MESSENGER," RIGHT?

27:52.504 --> 27:55.174
WELL, I WANT YOU TO DELIVER
A MESSAGE TO GOD.

27:55.207 --> 27:56.608
I THOUGHT YOU
DON'T BELIEVE IN HIM.

27:56.642 --> 27:58.077
I DON'T.

27:58.110 --> 28:01.580
BUT YOU DO, SO I WANT YOU
TO TELL HIM FROM ME

28:01.613 --> 28:03.415
THAT I THINK
HE'S AN [BLEEP]

28:03.449 --> 28:06.719
THAT IS BLASPHEMY, DANIEL.
IT IS A SIN.

28:06.753 --> 28:08.020
NO. NO. NO.

28:08.054 --> 28:11.090
A SIN -- A SIN
IS GIVING A BRAIN TUMOR

28:11.123 --> 28:14.093
TO A -- TO A KID WHO'S NEVER
DONE A BAD THING IN HIS LIFE.

28:14.126 --> 28:16.228
A SIN IS LETTING WHOEVER KILLED
JARED BAKER RUN FREE

28:16.262 --> 28:18.364
WHILE THAT BOY LIES DYING.

28:18.397 --> 28:21.433
DOES -- WHAT DOES --
DOES GOD ENJOY THIS?

28:21.467 --> 28:24.103
WATCHING MOTHERS
SOBBING THEIR EYES OUT?

28:24.136 --> 28:25.604
WHAT IS THAT, HIS THING?

28:25.637 --> 28:26.939
IS THAT ENTERTAINING
TO HIM?

28:26.973 --> 28:28.240
WHAT ARE WE?
IS THAT WHAT WE ARE --

28:28.274 --> 28:29.475
SOME SORT
OF ENTERTAINMENT?

28:31.643 --> 28:33.145
GIVE HIM THE MESSAGE.
T-TELL HIM.

28:33.179 --> 28:34.546
GO ON. TELL HIM --
TELL HIM --

28:34.580 --> 28:36.248
TELL HIM TO GO TO HELL.

28:38.384 --> 28:41.187
Ethan: THAT AUDIT IS ACCURATE
TO THE BEST OF MY KNOWLEDGE.

28:41.220 --> 28:44.023
WHAT ABOUT YOUR KNOWLEDGE
OF THE SEVEN CASH DEPOSITS

28:44.056 --> 28:45.257
MADE INTO YOUR ACCOUNT,

28:45.291 --> 28:47.126
EACH IN THE AMOUNT
OF $9,900,

28:47.159 --> 28:49.261
JUST A SQUEAK BELOW

28:49.295 --> 28:51.530
WHAT THE BANK
WOULD BE REQUIRED TO REPORT?

28:51.563 --> 28:53.499
I WON THAT MONEY
PLAYING POKER.

28:53.532 --> 28:54.566
I SEE.

28:54.600 --> 28:56.468
AND WITH
YOUR POKER WINNINGS,

28:56.502 --> 28:59.271
YOU DECIDED TO BUY YOURSELF A
ONE-WAY TICKET TO THE MALDIVES,

28:59.305 --> 29:02.641
A COUNTRY THAT JUST HAPPENS
TO HAVE NO EXTRADITION TREATY

29:02.674 --> 29:04.143
WITH THE UNITED STATES?

29:04.176 --> 29:06.145
I ALWAYS WANTED
TO GO THERE.

29:06.178 --> 29:09.281
JAIL IS NOTHING LIKE
THE MALDIVES, ETHAN.

29:09.315 --> 29:12.919
THERE ARE NO CRYSTAL-CLEAR
WATERS, NO PALM TREES,

29:12.952 --> 29:16.122
NO WAITERS FETCHING YOU
BRIGHTLY COLORED DRINKS.

29:21.593 --> 29:23.395
I WANT FULL IMMUNITY.

29:23.429 --> 29:24.997
THAT'S NOT GONNA HAPPEN.

29:25.031 --> 29:27.166
BUT IF YOU GIVE ME
THE NAME OF WHOEVER BRIBED YOU

29:27.199 --> 29:28.935
TO FALSIFY THIS AUDIT,

29:28.968 --> 29:31.437
I'LL ASK THE JUDGE
TO LET YOU PLEAD DOWN

29:31.470 --> 29:33.505
TO RECEIVING
IMPROPER BENEFITS.

29:33.539 --> 29:36.042
YOU'D GET OFF
WITH SIX MONTHS.

29:37.543 --> 29:39.511
THIS OFFER EXPIRES
IN 10 SECONDS.

29:39.545 --> 29:41.513
NINE...

29:41.547 --> 29:43.515
EIGHT...

29:43.549 --> 29:45.784
OKAY, OKAY, OKAY.

29:47.719 --> 29:50.689
I TOOK A BRIBE.

29:50.722 --> 29:53.625
WHO FROM?

30:01.500 --> 30:03.169
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

30:08.307 --> 30:09.775
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

30:09.808 --> 30:12.611
MR. SHELBY, COULD I SPEAK
TO YOU IN THE HALLWAY?

30:12.644 --> 30:14.080
Tom:
WHAT'S THIS ABOUT?

30:14.113 --> 30:16.082
IT WOULD BE BEST
IF WE SPOKE OUTSIDE.

30:16.115 --> 30:17.449
ANYTHING
YOU HAVE TO SAY,

30:17.483 --> 30:19.251
YOU CAN SAY
IN FRONT OF MY FAMILY.

30:19.285 --> 30:22.554
I'M PLACING YOU UNDER ARREST
FOR THE MURDER OF JARED BAKER.

30:22.588 --> 30:24.423
WHAT ARE YOU
THAT'S INSANE!

30:24.456 --> 30:26.792
YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
NO, LET GO OF HIM!

30:26.825 --> 30:27.960
ANYTHING YOU SAY, CAN AND
WILL BE USED AGAINST YOU
SANDY, DON'T. LAW.

30:27.994 --> 30:29.828
I'M COMING WITH YOU.

30:29.862 --> 30:31.363
YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO AN ATTORNEY.ITH KYLE.

30:31.397 --> 30:33.365
I CAN STAY HERE WITH KYLE.
GREG, TAKE YOUR MOM.

30:33.399 --> 30:35.834
NO, IF YOU CANNOT AFFORD
AN ATTORNEY,

30:35.868 --> 30:36.969
GOD KNOWS THE TRUTH.
HE'LL SET EVERYTHING RIGHT.

30:37.003 --> 30:38.104
DO YOU UNDERSTAND
THESE RIGHTS

30:38.137 --> 30:39.571
AS THEY HAVE BEEN
READ TO YOU?

30:39.605 --> 30:42.074
SO, HOW DO YOU --
HOW DO YOU KNOW TOM DID IT?

30:42.108 --> 30:44.643
PICKED UP THE I.R.S. AUDITOR
ON HIS WAY TO THE AIRPORT

30:44.676 --> 30:46.645
WITH A ONE-WAY TICKET
TO THE MALDIVES.

30:46.678 --> 30:48.147
SAID TOM BRIBED HIM
FOR A CLEAN AUDIT.

30:48.180 --> 30:49.882
YOU WERE RIGHT.
TOM WAS POCKETING ALL THE MONEY.

30:49.916 --> 30:51.150
OKAY,
BUT WHY KILL JARED?

30:51.183 --> 30:52.618
WELL, JARED
WAS ON TO THE SCAM.

30:52.651 --> 30:54.320
TOM FOUND THAT OUT
THE NIGHT BEFORE THE MURDER.

30:54.353 --> 30:55.687
LOOK,
WE GOT TO GET GOING.

30:55.721 --> 30:57.256
I'LL TELL YOU ALL ABOUT IT
IN THE CAR.

30:57.289 --> 30:58.958
W-W-- YOU'RE SURE THAT
NO ONE ELSE IS IN ON IT?

30:58.991 --> 31:02.461
UNTIL YOU'RE SURE,
I'M STAYING WITH KYLE.

31:02.494 --> 31:04.463
WHY WOULD I KILL JARED?
I LOVED HIM.

31:04.496 --> 31:07.633
WE GOT A WARRANT TO SEARCH
YOUR HOUSE, INCLUDING YOUR SAFE,

31:07.666 --> 31:09.868
AND WE FOUND RECORDS
OF THE CASH PAYMENTS

31:09.902 --> 31:11.703
YOU MADE
TO THE I.R.S. AUDITOR.

31:11.737 --> 31:13.705
I SWEAR TO GOD
I NEVER GAVE HIM ANYTHING.

31:13.739 --> 31:15.541
HE TOLD US ABOUT HOW YOU DID
YOUR RESEARCH ON HIM

31:15.574 --> 31:17.176
WHEN HE FIRST STARTED
THE AUDIT.

31:17.209 --> 31:19.145
YOU KNEW THAT HE HAD ALIMONY,
GAMBLING DEBTS.

31:19.178 --> 31:21.981
YOU KNEW THAT IF YOU OFFERED HIM
A BRIBE FOR A CLEAN AUDIT,

31:22.014 --> 31:24.150
THAHE'S LYING. IT.

31:24.183 --> 31:26.152
WE ALSO FOUND
THE INCORPORATION DOCUMENTS

31:26.185 --> 31:27.619
FOR THE SHELL ORGANIZATION

31:27.653 --> 31:29.121
THAT RUNS THE FAKE SCHOOL
IN AFGHANISTAN.

31:29.155 --> 31:31.523
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?
THE SCHOOL IS REAL.

31:31.557 --> 31:33.859
THE STATE DEPARTMENT
HAS NO RECORD

31:33.892 --> 31:36.695
OF A FOREIGN CHARITY OPERATING
A SCHOOL IN MAIMANA.

31:36.728 --> 31:39.698
WE SEND THEM
ALMOST $1 MILLION A YEAR.

31:39.731 --> 31:41.367
NO, YOU SEND
ALMOST $1 MILLION A YEAR

31:41.400 --> 31:44.303
TO AN ACCOUNT IN YOUR NAME
AT THE BANK OF KABUL.

31:44.336 --> 31:45.938
FROM KABUL,
IT'S TRANSFERRED

31:45.972 --> 31:48.374
TO THE EVER-POPULAR
CAYMAN ISLANDS.

31:48.407 --> 31:51.710
NOW I KNOW WHY YOU WERE SO EAGER
TO PUT US ONTO SHANE FLANNERY.

31:51.743 --> 31:53.045
NO.
I WOULD NEVER DO THAT.

31:53.079 --> 31:54.746
YOU WERE RAKING IT IN
LIKE CRAZY,

31:54.780 --> 31:57.349
UNTIL JARED BAKER FOUND OUT
THAT THE SCHOOL WAS FAKE.

31:57.383 --> 31:59.451
AND HE CALLED ETHAN
OVER AT THE I.R.S.

31:59.485 --> 32:01.887
ETHAN CALLED YOU
AND SAID YOU HAD A PROBLEM.

32:01.920 --> 32:03.455
AND THEN,
ACCORDING TO ETHAN,

32:03.489 --> 32:07.093
YOUR EXACT WORDS WERE,
"I'LL TAKE CARE OF IT."

32:08.760 --> 32:10.062
I GUESS YOU DID.

32:11.863 --> 32:15.067
I NEED TO FIND TOM
A LAWYER.

32:15.101 --> 32:17.069
SANDY, LET GREG
MAKE THE CALLS.

32:17.103 --> 32:18.404
YOU NEED TO REST.

32:18.437 --> 32:19.972
SHE'S RIGHT, MOM.
LET ME TAKE YOU HOME.

32:20.006 --> 32:21.707
NO.
I CAN'T LEAVE KYLE.

32:21.740 --> 32:22.908
I'LL BE RIGHT HERE.

32:22.941 --> 32:24.743
I'LL CALL YOU
THE SECOND HE WAKES UP.

32:24.776 --> 32:25.777
I'LL STAY, TOO.

32:28.280 --> 32:30.582
THANK SURE.NIKKI.

32:32.751 --> 32:34.586
AND THANK YOU,
DR. PIERCE.

32:45.964 --> 32:48.567
DR. PIERCE,
IF IT'S ALL RIGHT...

32:48.600 --> 32:51.737
I'D LIKE SOME TIME ALONE...

32:51.770 --> 32:53.205
TO PRAY.

32:53.239 --> 32:56.208
OF COURSE
SHE WANTS TIME ALONE...

32:56.242 --> 32:58.377
BECAUSE AS SOON
AS YOU LEAVE THE ROOM,

32:58.410 --> 33:00.612
SHE IS GOING TO KILL
THE BOY.

33:04.150 --> 33:06.918
NIKKI, IF IT'S ALL THE SAME
TO YOU...

33:08.420 --> 33:10.022
...I'M GONNA STAY.

33:17.163 --> 33:19.431
LOOK AT HER.

33:19.465 --> 33:22.634
THE SOUL OF PIETY
AND DEVOTION.

33:22.668 --> 33:24.970
BUT DOESN'T IT
BOTHER YOU

33:25.003 --> 33:28.207
HOW EAGER SHE HAS BEEN TO GET
EVERYBODY OUT OF THE ROOM?

33:30.276 --> 33:32.744
THE BOY
WAS VERY CURIOUS

33:32.778 --> 33:35.247
AS TO WHY
YOU WERE TALKING TO HER.

33:35.281 --> 33:38.550
MAYBE HE HAD ASKED
TOO MANY QUESTIONS...

33:38.584 --> 33:39.785
AND SHE PUSHED HIM.

33:39.818 --> 33:41.320
AND THINK --

33:41.353 --> 33:44.323
THINK OF THAT TAX MAN
FLYING OFF TO THE MALDIVES.

33:44.356 --> 33:46.325
OF ALL THE COUNTRIES
IN THE WORLD,

33:46.358 --> 33:49.461
WHY WOULD HE CHOOSE
A ROMANTIC TROPICAL ISLAND?

33:49.495 --> 33:53.232
UNLESS HE WASN'T PLANNING
TO GO THERE ALONE.

33:54.800 --> 33:59.838
YES, SHE IS
VERY BEAUTIFUL, NO?

33:59.871 --> 34:01.940
JUST THE PERFECT TYPE
OF WOMAN

34:01.973 --> 34:05.277
A LONELY TAX MAN WOULD DREAM
OF RUNNING AWAY WITH.

34:05.311 --> 34:06.678
THAT'S STILL NOT PROOF.

34:06.712 --> 34:08.447
WHAT?

34:08.480 --> 34:10.649
N-NOTHING.

34:10.682 --> 34:14.286
IT'S HARDLY ENOUGH TO GET HER
BURNED AT THE STAKE,

34:14.320 --> 34:17.523
BUT IT'S MORE
THAN THE BRITISH HAD ON ME.

34:17.556 --> 34:19.991
Nikki:
PLEASE, DR. PIERCE,

34:20.025 --> 34:22.094
I'D REALLY LIKE
SOME TIME ALONE WITH KYLE.

34:23.895 --> 34:25.697
[ SIGHS ]

34:25.731 --> 34:28.434
WHAT ARE YOU GOING TO DO?

34:36.708 --> 34:39.645
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

34:44.116 --> 34:47.753
[ BEEPING, FLATLINE ]

34:47.786 --> 34:50.055
WHAT?
W-WHAT IS THAT?

34:50.088 --> 34:52.324
WHY IS IT MAKING
THAT SOUND?

34:52.358 --> 34:55.561
[ FLATLINE ]

34:57.263 --> 34:58.597
HE'S GONE.

34:58.630 --> 35:01.400
WH-- WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

35:01.433 --> 35:02.734
NO. HE'S BREATHING.

35:02.768 --> 35:04.102
THIS MONITORS
NEUROELECTRICAL ACTIVITY.

35:05.471 --> 35:07.005
KYLE'S BRAIN-DEAD.

35:07.038 --> 35:09.341
OH, MY GOD.

35:09.375 --> 35:12.110
I-I-I HAVE TO CALL
HIS PARENTS.

35:12.144 --> 35:15.347
[ FLATLINE ]

35:15.381 --> 35:19.618
OH, SORRY. I MUST HAVE, UH,
KNOCKED THIS OUT BY MISTAKE.

35:22.488 --> 35:24.623
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

35:24.656 --> 35:26.525
[ STAMMERS ]

35:26.558 --> 35:27.726
[ BEEPING ]

35:27.759 --> 35:29.261
Tom isn't the killer.

35:29.295 --> 35:31.029
IT'WHAT?KI.

35:31.062 --> 35:32.398
She says she loves Kyle.

35:32.431 --> 35:34.166
BUT WHEN HE DIED,
SHE DIDN'T EVEN LOOK AT HIM.

35:34.200 --> 35:35.534
She just took off
like a bat out of hell.

35:35.567 --> 35:37.035
No, no, no, no.E DIED?

35:37.068 --> 35:38.370
THAT WAS JUST PRETEND.

35:38.404 --> 35:39.671
WHA-- DANIEL, WHAT ARE
YOU TALKING ABOUT?

35:39.705 --> 35:41.173
It was all Nikki --

35:41.207 --> 35:43.809
KILLING JARED,
PUSHING KYLE DOWN THE STAIRS.

35:43.842 --> 35:45.477
She's been waiting to get him
alone so she can finish the job.

35:45.511 --> 35:47.679
YOU'VE GOT TO STOP HER
BEFORE SHE LEAVES THE COUNTRY.

35:47.713 --> 35:49.448
DO YOU HAVE
ANY PROOF OF THIS?

35:49.481 --> 35:51.450
N-N-Okay.UT --

35:51.483 --> 35:52.884
THEN WE NEED TO PUT
A TAIL ON HER,

35:52.918 --> 35:54.152
FIND OUT WHERE SHE'S HEADED
IN SUCH A HURRY.

35:54.186 --> 35:56.355
RIGHT.

36:00.659 --> 36:02.628
[ DOOR OPENS ]

36:02.661 --> 36:04.863
HEY, NEED A HAND
WITH THOSE?

36:06.932 --> 36:08.834
Ethan: I ALREADY TOLD YOU
THE WHOLE STORY.

36:08.867 --> 36:10.702
THE PROBLEM IS
THAT NIKKI ATKINS

36:10.736 --> 36:12.704
IS TELLING US
A DIFFERENT VERSION.

36:12.738 --> 36:16.208
AND IN HERS, THE AFGHAN SCAM,
FRAMING TOM SHELBY,

36:16.242 --> 36:19.811
MURDERING JARED BAKER --
THAT WAS ALL YOU.

36:19.845 --> 36:22.080
SHE SAYS YOU BLACKMAILED HER
INTO GOING ALONG WITH IT.

36:22.113 --> 36:24.216
[ CHUCKLES ]

36:24.250 --> 36:26.084
YOU'RE MAKING THAT UP
TO TRAP ME.

36:26.117 --> 36:28.354
WE PICKED HER UP AT A BANK
WITH TWO SACKS FULL OF CASH.

36:28.387 --> 36:29.721
HER NEXT STOP
WAS THE AIRPORT.

36:29.755 --> 36:32.090
SHE HAD HER BOARDING PASS
ALL PRINTED UP.

36:32.123 --> 36:36.061
YEAH, SEE, EXCEPT SHE WAS
NOT GOING TO THE MALDIVES.

36:43.201 --> 36:45.337
[ SIGHS ]

36:45.371 --> 36:48.740
IT WAS ALL HER.
THE SCAM, EVERYTHING.

36:48.774 --> 36:50.742
SHE KILLED JARED.

36:53.979 --> 36:55.947
[ SIGHS ]

36:55.981 --> 36:59.685
I MET HER WHEN I STARTED
THE AUDIT ON HAVEN HOUSE.

37:05.291 --> 37:07.192
I ACTUALLY
LET MYSELF BELIEVE

37:07.225 --> 37:09.428
IT WAS ABOUT
MORE THAN BUSINESS.

37:12.731 --> 37:15.033
ONCE SHE WAS SURE
THAT SHE HAD ME,

37:15.066 --> 37:17.035
SHE TOLD ME
ABOUT HER SCAM,

37:17.068 --> 37:21.473
OFFERED TO CUT ME IN 50/50 IF
I MADE THE AUDIT COME OUT CLEAN.

37:21.507 --> 37:23.642
HOW'D SHE GET THE CON GOING
TO BEGIN WITH?

37:23.675 --> 37:25.644
SHE HEARD ABOUT THIS PLACE
WHERE MORONS

37:25.677 --> 37:29.748
SIGNED OVER FORTUNES
AND DIDN'T ASK QUESTIONS.

37:29.781 --> 37:34.753
SHE SHOWED UP, PRETENDING
TO BE A LOST LITTLE LAMB,

37:34.786 --> 37:39.491
HOOKED UP WITH THE OLDER BROTHER
SO SHE COULD BE ON THE INSIDE.

37:39.525 --> 37:40.592
WHAT ABOUT THE SCHOOL
IN AFGHANISTAN?

37:40.626 --> 37:42.294
WHERE'D THAT COME FROM?

37:42.328 --> 37:44.996
SHE SCANNED SOME PICTURES
FROM NATIONAL GEOGRAPHIC,

37:45.030 --> 37:47.165
PUT TOGETHER A WEBSITE,
AND E-MAILED TOM,

37:47.198 --> 37:48.434
ASKING FOR HIS HELP.

37:50.936 --> 37:53.171
SEEMED LIKE
WE PULLED IT OFF.

37:53.204 --> 37:54.773
UNTIL JARED BAKER
STARTED ASKING QUESTIONS

37:54.806 --> 37:56.174
ABOUT THE SCHOOL
IN AFGHANISTAN.

37:56.207 --> 37:58.510
YEAH,
AFTER I TALKED TO JARED,

37:58.544 --> 38:03.315
I CALLED UP NIKKI, AND I TOLD
HER WE HAD A PROBLEM.

38:03.349 --> 38:06.685
NEXT DAY,
JARED TURNS UP DEAD.

38:06.718 --> 38:09.321
I CALLED HER, AND I SAID,
"WHAT THE [BLEEP] IS GOING ON?

38:09.355 --> 38:11.022
NO ONE'S
SUPPOSED TO GET HURT."

38:11.056 --> 38:14.960
SHE TOLD ME TO KEEP QUIET
AND TO GET OUT OF TOWN.

38:14.993 --> 38:16.962
SO I WENT HOME,
AND I GOT MY BAGS.

38:16.995 --> 38:18.330
YOU GUYS PICKED ME UP.

38:18.364 --> 38:21.833
AND THAT IS THE ENTIRE STORY.
I SWEAR.

38:21.867 --> 38:25.837
JUST ONE PROBLEM --
IT'S YOUR WORD AGAINST HERS.

38:25.871 --> 38:29.575
I MIGHT BE AN IDIOT,
BUT I AM NOT STUPID.

38:31.242 --> 38:33.545
CHECK THE LINING
IN MY SUITCASE.

38:33.579 --> 38:36.548
THERE'S A FLASH DRIVE
WITH SOME SOUND FILES ON IT.

38:36.582 --> 38:39.050
ONE THING YOU LEARN
WHEN YOU WORK FOR THE I.R.S.,

38:39.084 --> 38:41.853
YOUR WHOLE LIFE IS THE VALUE
OF KEEPING GOOD RECORDS.

38:45.591 --> 38:47.726
NIKKI: They aren't buying
that Shane killed Jared.

38:47.759 --> 38:49.861
Oh, baby, calm down.

38:49.895 --> 38:51.563
Okay.
We're going to be all right.

38:51.597 --> 38:53.131
I've got the room all booked

38:53.164 --> 38:55.000
on the most beautiful beach
in the Maldives.

38:55.033 --> 38:57.969
KYLE:
Nikki, what's going on?
Who are you talking to?

38:58.003 --> 38:59.471
NIKKI:
Hey. I-I got to go.

38:59.505 --> 39:01.473
No, I think Kyle heard me.
Okay.

39:01.507 --> 39:03.775
I love you.
I'll see you at the airport.

39:03.809 --> 39:05.944
KYLE WANTED TO KNOW
WHY YOU WERE TALKING TO US.

39:05.977 --> 39:07.979
THAT'S WHY
HE KNOCKED ON YOUR DOOR.

39:08.013 --> 39:09.581
Kate:
BUT HE OVERHEARD TOO MUCH,

39:09.615 --> 39:11.817
AND THAT'S WHY YOU PUSHED HIM
DOWN THE STAIRS.

39:11.850 --> 39:13.318
DO YOU THINK I DON'T KNOW

39:13.351 --> 39:15.854
THAT A SOUND RECORDING
CAN BE MANIPULATED?

39:17.423 --> 39:19.991
DO YOU EVEN KNOW THAT
YOU'RE DOING SATAN'S WORK?

39:22.293 --> 39:25.764
PLEASE, GOD, I PRAY THAT YOU
WILL FORGIVE THESE PEOPLE

39:25.797 --> 39:27.098
FOR THEIR BLINDNESS.

39:27.132 --> 39:29.267
I PRAY THAT YOU WILL
SHOW THEM THE TRUTH.

39:29.300 --> 39:31.403
WHILE YOU'RE AT IT,
YOU MIGHT WANT TO ALSO PRAY

39:31.437 --> 39:34.406
FOR A JUDGE WHO DOESN'T
BELIEVE IN THE DEATH PENALTY.

39:36.041 --> 39:38.510
Dr. Goldsby:
IT'S A MIRACLE, REALLY.

39:38.544 --> 39:40.512
KYLE'S AWAKE
AND EATING CHOCOLATE PUDDING

39:40.546 --> 39:41.680
LIKE THERE'S NO TOMORROW.

39:41.713 --> 39:43.014
HOW MUCH TISSUE DAMAGE?

39:43.048 --> 39:44.215
SOME SWELLING.

39:44.249 --> 39:45.851
HE'LL NEED TO TAKE IT EASY
FOR A WHILE,

39:45.884 --> 39:47.419
BUT HE SHOULD MAKE
A GOOD RECOVERY.

39:47.453 --> 39:48.520
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

39:55.894 --> 39:59.865
THAT MESSAGE YOU SENT GOD
MUST HAVE DONE THE TRICK.

39:59.898 --> 40:03.034
SOMETIMES HE NEEDS
A KICK IN THE PANTS.

40:03.068 --> 40:05.871
PEOPLE MAKE AMAZING RECOVERIES
ALL THE TIME

40:05.904 --> 40:08.640
WITH NO HELP
FROM SOME NONEXISTENT DEITY.

40:08.674 --> 40:12.210
IF HE DOESN'T EXIST, THEN WHY
WOULD YOU SEND HIM A MESSAGE?

40:13.712 --> 40:15.714
BECAUSE I'M A STARK,
RAVING LUNATIC.

40:18.484 --> 40:21.453
LOOK, ARE CLOSING
HAVEN HOUSE,

40:21.487 --> 40:23.421
BUT WE'RE KEEPING
THE BROKEN PROMISE,

40:23.455 --> 40:25.190
OPENING A SCHOOL
IN AFGHANISTAN.

40:26.424 --> 40:28.093
I KNOW IT'S WHAT GOD WANTS.

40:28.126 --> 40:30.829
YOU'RE STILL HEARING A VOICE
EVEN AFTER THE OPERATION?

40:30.862 --> 40:34.332
NOT AN ACTUAL VOICE IN MY HEAD
LIKE BEFORE.

40:34.365 --> 40:37.669
BUT I STILL HEAR GOD
EVERY SECOND...

40:37.703 --> 40:39.771
THE WAY ANYBODY CAN
IF THEY JUST LISTEN.

40:46.512 --> 40:49.515
HERE.

40:52.718 --> 40:55.253
MAYBE THIS WILL BUY A FEW BOOKS
FOR THE NEW SCHOOL.

40:58.456 --> 40:59.858
WOW!

40:59.891 --> 41:01.727
THAT'S A LOT OF BOOKS.

41:03.394 --> 41:05.697
DOES THIS MEAN
YOU BELIEVE IN GOD NOW?

41:05.731 --> 41:07.833
ABSOLUTELY NOT.

41:09.000 --> 41:10.902
BUT I BELIEVE IN YOU.

41:12.671 --> 41:16.842
I GOT SOMETHING
FOR YOU, TOO.

41:18.744 --> 41:21.713
KYLE, WHAT KIND
OF PRESENT IS THAT?

41:21.747 --> 41:23.882
I THINK DR. PIERCE
WILL APPRECIATE IT.

41:23.915 --> 41:25.917
[ CHUCKLES ]
